 PURPOSE OF ART</span><hr size=1> I have some friends who just can't understand why I take this much time every day doing something that is, in their perspectives, useless.  (I call it the &quot;Not a Real Job&quot; syndrome, and I've decided it's a disease on THEIR side of the conversation, not mine.)<br>
<br>
Still, it's sometimes hard to articulate what it is that Art brings to the world, and in the more focused view, to the Self.<br>
<br>
What is, to you, the purpose of Art?  What has Art brought to you and your life that wasn't there before; wasn't in the world before?<br>
<br>
(forgive the Deep Thoughts this evening -- for some reason, i went to bed at 8:30 p.m. and woke up at TWO A.M., fully awake.  My body's weeeeeird.)<br>
