<br>
Up until recently (my husband is currently laid off), I have been lucky enough to be able to pursue my art without many money worries, but that does not mean that I haven't contributed emotionally, or financially to the family. Many people just don't get that. If you don't get in the car and drive a distance to an office, work the proverbial 9-5, come home drained and then have to rush around to do whatever else it is you have to do, it's not a 'real' job. <!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://www.molalla.net/~mwheeler/Images/Emoticons/roll_eyes.gif"/><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--> I think that many of those people wish they were in the position, or had the ability to do what they wanted. That's what I chalk the comments up to anyway.<br>
<br>
To me the purpose of art is to bring beauty to the world. To give others the ability to see what they may not have seen before. And it makes me happy when someone falls in love with one of my pieces of art and wants to have it. Not because I'm selling it, but because it has captured their interest and makes them happy. That makes me happy. Art has brought to my life the ability to continue to be creative, to relax and to enjoy what I do. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub98.ezboard.com/fiqzinefrm7.showPrevMessage?topicID=5.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub98.ezboard.com/fiqzinefrm7.showNextMessage?topicID=5.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub98.ezboard.com/fiqzinefrm7.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=5.topic&index=2><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/addReply1.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub98.ezboard.com/fiqzinefrm7.emailToFriend?topicID=5.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub98.ezboard.com/fiqzinefrm7.threadControl?topicID=5.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/deleteThreadFire.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub98.ezboard.com/fiqzinefrm7.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=5.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/subscribe.gif width=20 height=20 border=0 alt="Click to receive email notification of replies"> Click to receive email notification of replies</a> <br>  <a href=http://pub98.ezboard.com/fiqzinefrm7.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=5.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/unsubscribe.gif width=20 height=20 border=0 alt="Cl